for loop : It is used to reduce the line of code. It is same as while loop

Syntax:
1:

	for(initialization; condition; inc/dec)
	{
		statements;
	}
2:	
	initialization;
	for(; condition; inc/dec )
	{
		Statements;
	}

3:
	initialization;
	for(; condition;  )
	{
		Statements;
		inc/dec;
	}	

4: Infinite for Loop
	for(; ;)
	{
		stetements;
	}
